UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc7='Fired Up and Not So Good To Go.',details_loc7='Leave it to the Dark Irons to work with Ragnaros\' toadies and worse. You can bet that insane Twilight\'s Hammer cult is behind the lot of this!$B$BTime to end their attacks on Ironforge once and for all. Oh, and tell Commander Cragfist what\'s happened here when we return; I\'ll need to work on getting the city and its good people back in order.',objectives_loc7='Slay Grand Ambassador Flamelash and inform Commander Cragfist in Ironforge.',offerrewardtext_loc7='Dark Iron dwarves and Ragnaros the Firelord, ye say? At the behest of the Cult o\' Twilight\'s Hammer? Well done! Ironforge is in yer debt. ' WHERE entry=27122; /* title: Fired Up and Not So Good To Go. */ /* details: Leave it to the Dark Irons to work with Ragnaros\' toadies and worse. You can bet that insane Twilight\'s Hammer cult is behind the lot of this!$B$BTime to end their attacks on Ironforge once and for all. Oh, and tell Commander Cragfist what\'s happened here when we return; I\'ll need to work on getting the city and its good people back in order. */ /* objectives: Slay Grand Ambassador Flamelash and inform Commander Cragfist in Ironforge. */ /* offerrewardtext: Dark Iron dwarves and Ragnaros the Firelord, ye say? At the behest of the Cult o\' Twilight\'s Hammer? Well done! Ironforge is in yer debt. */
