UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc7='The Elements Cry Out',details_loc7='Do you feel it, $c?  The elements are uneasy. We members of the Earthen Ring have struggled to find the cause of the unrest.  Thus far we have been unsuccessful and now turn to others that may aid us.  Speak with Erunak Stonespeaker in Stormwind and see how you might be able to aid us.',objectives_loc7='Speak with Erunak Stonespeaker in Stormwind.',offerrewardtext_loc7='I\'m glad you\'ve come, $c.  These are troublesome times and we could use all the help we can get. ' WHERE entry=27307; /* title: The Elements Cry Out */ /* details: Do you feel it, $c?  The elements are uneasy. We members of the Earthen Ring have struggled to find the cause of the unrest.  Thus far we have been unsuccessful and now turn to others that may aid us.  Speak with Erunak Stonespeaker in Stormwind and see how you might be able to aid us. */ /* objectives: Speak with Erunak Stonespeaker in Stormwind. */ /* offerrewardtext: I\'m glad you\'ve come, $c.  These are troublesome times and we could use all the help we can get. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc7='The Elements Cry Out',details_loc7='Do you feel it, $c?  The elements are uneasy. We members of the Earthen Ring have struggled to find the cause of the unrest.  Thus far we have been unsuccessful and now turn to others that may aid us.  Speak with Earthmender Norsala in Orgrimmar and see what tasks she may have for you.',objectives_loc7='Speak to Earthmender Norsala in Orgrimmar.',offerrewardtext_loc7='I\'m glad you\'ve come, $c.  These are troublesome times and we could use all the help we can get. ' WHERE entry=27308; /* title: The Elements Cry Out */ /* details: Do you feel it, $c?  The elements are uneasy. We members of the Earthen Ring have struggled to find the cause of the unrest.  Thus far we have been unsuccessful and now turn to others that may aid us.  Speak with Earthmender Norsala in Orgrimmar and see what tasks she may have for you. */ /* objectives: Speak to Earthmender Norsala in Orgrimmar. */ /* offerrewardtext: I\'m glad you\'ve come, $c.  These are troublesome times and we could use all the help we can get. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc7='What\'s Shaking in Ironforge',details_loc7='Things have grown worse in Ironforge, $n.  Please, speak with Stormcaller Mylra in Ironforge and see if you can lend a hand in some way.',objectives_loc7='Speak with Stormcaller Mylra in Ironforge.',offerrewardtext_loc7='It is good that you\'ve come, $n.  We need all the help we can get with the situation here. ' WHERE entry=27473; /* title: What\'s Shaking in Ironforge */ /* details: Things have grown worse in Ironforge, $n.  Please, speak with Stormcaller Mylra in Ironforge and see if you can lend a hand in some way. */ /* objectives: Speak with Stormcaller Mylra in Ironforge. */ /* offerrewardtext: It is good that you\'ve come, $n.  We need all the help we can get with the situation here. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc7='The Wildhammer',details_loc7='No doubt you\'ve felt the earthquakes.  You may even have seen elementals attacking the lands or towns.  The Earthen Ring struggles to understand what is going on.  We\'ve been fortunate to gain assistance from the Wildhammer shamans.$b$bGavan Grayfeather is in Stormwind Keep to help coordinate our efforts with the various faction leaders.  Speak to him and see what you may learn about these events, $n.',objectives_loc7='Speak to Gavan Grayfeather in Stormwind Keep.',offerrewardtext_loc7='Well met, $c.  I am Gavan Grayfeather, emissary of the Wildhammer shaman. There is much work to be done.  The leaders fear for their citizens, as many have turned to cults.  We shaman are concerned with the elemental unrest. Our advice to you, $c, is to be vigilant.  Help where you can, be it calming the people or putting the elementals at rest.  There is plenty to do. ' WHERE entry=27540; /* title: The Wildhammer */ /* details: No doubt you\'ve felt the earthquakes.  You may even have seen elementals attacking the lands or towns.  The Earthen Ring struggles to understand what is going on.  We\'ve been fortunate to gain assistance from the Wildhammer shamans.$b$bGavan Grayfeather is in Stormwind Keep to help coordinate our efforts with the various faction leaders.  Speak to him and see what you may learn about these events, $n. */ /* objectives: Speak to Gavan Grayfeather in Stormwind Keep. */ /* offerrewardtext: Well met, $c.  I am Gavan Grayfeather, emissary of the Wildhammer shaman. There is much work to be done.  The leaders fear for their citizens, as many have turned to cults.  We shaman are concerned with the elemental unrest. Our advice to you, $c, is to be vigilant.  Help where you can, be it calming the people or putting the elementals at rest.  There is plenty to do. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc7='Speak with Captain Anton',details_loc7='No doubt you\'ve felt the earthquakes.  You may even have seen elementals attacking the lands or towns. We have sent many of our brightest minds to Nagrand to commune with the elements.$b$bBut there is still much work to be done here.  Stormwind Guards are being overwhelmed with citizens worried about their loved ones.$b$bPlease, $c, speak with Captain Anton in Stormwind Keep and see how you might assist him.',objectives_loc7='Speak with Captain Anton in Stormwind Keep.',offerrewardtext_loc7='King\'s honor, $c.  I am Captain Anton.  I am leading the investigation into the cultists that have appeared in Stormwind. ' WHERE entry=27546; /* title: Speak with Captain Anton */ /* details: No doubt you\'ve felt the earthquakes.  You may even have seen elementals attacking the lands or towns. We have sent many of our brightest minds to Nagrand to commune with the elements.$b$bBut there is still much work to be done here.  Stormwind Guards are being overwhelmed with citizens worried about their loved ones.$b$bPlease, $c, speak with Captain Anton in Stormwind Keep and see how you might assist him. */ /* objectives: Speak with Captain Anton in Stormwind Keep. */ /* offerrewardtext: King\'s honor, $c.  I am Captain Anton.  I am leading the investigation into the cultists that have appeared in Stormwind. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc7='A Gathering in Outland',details_loc7='Greetings, $c.  The elements have grown more restless and we seem to be making little progress to a solution for this problem.  Some of our wisest shaman have gathered in Nagrand at the Throne of Elements to discuss what ails our land.$b$bHead to the Throne of Elements and speak with Gavan Grayfeather, he will surely have some task for you.',objectives_loc7='Speak with Gavan Grayfeather at the Throne of Elements in Nagrand.',offerrewardtext_loc7='It is good to see you, $n.  Here at the Throne of Elements we may be able to uncover what ails Azeroth. ' WHERE entry=27566; /* title: A Gathering in Outland */ /* details: Greetings, $c.  The elements have grown more restless and we seem to be making little progress to a solution for this problem.  Some of our wisest shaman have gathered in Nagrand at the Throne of Elements to discuss what ails our land.$b$bHead to the Throne of Elements and speak with Gavan Grayfeather, he will surely have some task for you. */ /* objectives: Speak with Gavan Grayfeather at the Throne of Elements in Nagrand. */ /* offerrewardtext: It is good to see you, $n.  Here at the Throne of Elements we may be able to uncover what ails Azeroth. */
UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc7='The Situation So Far',details_loc7='No doubt you\'ve felt the earthquakes.  You may even have seen elementals attacking the lands or towns.  The Earthen Ring struggles to understand what is going on.  We\'ve been fortunate to have one of the greatest shaman as our Warchief.$b$bThrall has been consulting with his advisors, and we don\'t want to interrupt his council.  But perhaps our brother, Gotura Fourwinds, has learned of Thrall\'s plans.',objectives_loc7='Speak with Gotura Fourwinds in Grommash Hold in Orgrimmar.',offerrewardtext_loc7='Greetings, $c.  The situation here is tense.  The elements are restless and the people are scared and confused.  The Warchief is trying to find a semblance of balance between leading the people and protecting Azeroth.  Though it seems he will soon be leaving us to travel to Nagrand and gain insight about the elementals. Regardless of the Warchief\'s choice, we still must do what we can.  Help calm the populace, scour the lands for rogue elementals.  These tasks will surely help our cause. ' WHERE entry=27570; /* title: The Situation So Far */ /* details: No doubt you\'ve felt the earthquakes.  You may even have seen elementals attacking the lands or towns.  The Earthen Ring struggles to understand what is going on.  We\'ve been fortunate to have one of the greatest shaman as our Warchief.$b$bThrall has been consulting with his advisors, and we don\'t want to interrupt his council.  But perhaps our brother, Gotura Fourwinds, has learned of Thrall\'s plans. */ /* objectives: Speak with Gotura Fourwinds in Grommash Hold in Orgrimmar. */ /* offerrewardtext: Greetings, $c.  The situation here is tense.  The elements are restless and the people are scared and confused.  The Warchief is trying to find a semblance of balance between leading the people and protecting Azeroth.  Though it seems he will soon be leaving us to travel to Nagrand and gain insight about the elementals. Regardless of the Warchief\'s choice, we still must do what we can.  Help calm the populace, scour the lands for rogue elementals.  These tasks will surely help our cause. */
