UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc7='Show Me Your Papers',details_loc7='After your work in dealing with the Twilight\'s Hammer cult, Captain Anton recommended you for a delicate assignment.$B$BMy men recently discovered a group of cultists attempting to sneak into the city. The flow of traffic into the Stormwind has come to a halt. The king has decreed that all visitors must be searched before they can enter the gates. Take this copy of his proclamation and read it to the people assembled at the front gates, then assist the guards there in searching those who wish to enter.',objectives_loc7='Go to the front gates of Stormwind, read King Wrynn\'s Proclamation and search 5 Stormwind Citizens. Keep anything suspicious that you find.',offerrewardtext_loc7='So there were more cultists waiting to be admitted to the city? It\'s a good thing that you caught them, $n. Reading over the note that you found, it seems they\'re planning something big. ' WHERE entry=27741; /* title: Show Me Your Papers */ /* details: After your work in dealing with the Twilight\'s Hammer cult, Captain Anton recommended you for a delicate assignment.$B$BMy men recently discovered a group of cultists attempting to sneak into the city. The flow of traffic into the Stormwind has come to a halt. The king has decreed that all visitors must be searched before they can enter the gates. Take this copy of his proclamation and read it to the people assembled at the front gates, then assist the guards there in searching those who wish to enter. */ /* objectives: Go to the front gates of Stormwind, read King Wrynn\'s Proclamation and search 5 Stormwind Citizens. Keep anything suspicious that you find. */ /* offerrewardtext: So there were more cultists waiting to be admitted to the city? It\'s a good thing that you caught them, $n. Reading over the note that you found, it seems they\'re planning something big. */
