UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc7='Back Under Cover',details_loc7='The cultists seem assured of their victory, even as we detain more and more of them. We must find out more about the ritual mentioned by the cultist you questioned.$B$BThese rituals seem to be the core of the cult\'s plan to attack Stormwind. I\'m going to give you one of the robes taken from the arrested cultists. Put it on and go back to the cultist outpost at Mirror Lake Orchard in Elwynn Forest and see if you can get the cultists there to let you in on the plan.',objectives_loc7='Put on your Recruit\'s Robe, go to Mirror Lake Orchard and get the Book of Incantations from Overseer Sylandra. Read from the Book of Incantations near the Cultist Altar to practice the ritual.',offerrewardtext_loc7='You need to familiarize yourself with the portal ritual quickly. We need to send as many teams into Stormwind as we can. They\'re discovering and arresting more of our brothers each day. ' WHERE entry=27767; /* title: Back Under Cover */ /* details: The cultists seem assured of their victory, even as we detain more and more of them. We must find out more about the ritual mentioned by the cultist you questioned.$B$BThese rituals seem to be the core of the cult\'s plan to attack Stormwind. I\'m going to give you one of the robes taken from the arrested cultists. Put it on and go back to the cultist outpost at Mirror Lake Orchard in Elwynn Forest and see if you can get the cultists there to let you in on the plan. */ /* objectives: Put on your Recruit\'s Robe, go to Mirror Lake Orchard and get the Book of Incantations from Overseer Sylandra. Read from the Book of Incantations near the Cultist Altar to practice the ritual. */ /* offerrewardtext: You need to familiarize yourself with the portal ritual quickly. We need to send as many teams into Stormwind as we can. They\'re discovering and arresting more of our brothers each day. */
