UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc7='I Said the Words...',details_loc7='Now that you\'re familiar with the ritual, it\'s time for you to perform it in the city. Dozens of our brethren have already made their way to the ritual sites.$B$BI want you to visit the portal ritual sites on the second level of the Drag, in the Valley of Honor near the Hall of the Brave, and near Orgrimmar\'s west gate. The teams there will have made most of the preparations and all you need to do is read the last part of the incantation from the book.$B$BVery soon the city will be consumed in flame.',objectives_loc7='Disrupt the cultist rituals in the Drag, the Valley of Honor, and near the city\'s West Gate by reading the incorrect words from the Book of Incantations.',offerrewardtext_loc7='You\'ve brought many of these traitors to justice, $n, and yet their numbers keep growing. I fear we won\'t be able to stomp out all these rituals in time... ' WHERE entry=27799; /* title: I Said the Words... */ /* details: Now that you\'re familiar with the ritual, it\'s time for you to perform it in the city. Dozens of our brethren have already made their way to the ritual sites.$B$BI want you to visit the portal ritual sites on the second level of the Drag, in the Valley of Honor near the Hall of the Brave, and near Orgrimmar\'s west gate. The teams there will have made most of the preparations and all you need to do is read the last part of the incantation from the book.$B$BVery soon the city will be consumed in flame. */ /* objectives: Disrupt the cultist rituals in the Drag, the Valley of Honor, and near the city\'s West Gate by reading the incorrect words from the Book of Incantations. */ /* offerrewardtext: You\'ve brought many of these traitors to justice, $n, and yet their numbers keep growing. I fear we won\'t be able to stomp out all these rituals in time... */
