UPDATE locales_quest SET title_loc7='Back Under Cover',details_loc7='The cultists seem assured of their victory, although we have captured many of them. We must find out more about the ritual mentioned by the cultist you questioned.$B$BThese rituals must be the core of their plans to attack Orgrimmar.$B$BTake one of the robes from the arrested cultists; it\'s not like they\'re going to need them anymore. Put it on and go back to the cultist outpost at the Jaggedswine Farm in Durotar and see what you can learn about these rituals and their place in the cult\'s plans.',objectives_loc7='Put on your Recruit\'s Robe, go to the Jaggedswine Farm and get the Book of Incantations from Overseer Jintak. Read from the Book of Incantations near the Cultist Altar to practice the ritual.',offerrewardtext_loc7='You need to familiarize yourself with the portal ritual quickly. We\'ve sent dozens of brothers into the city, but only so many can evade capture. We\'re relying on you, $n. ' WHERE entry=27800; /* title: Back Under Cover */ /* details: The cultists seem assured of their victory, although we have captured many of them. We must find out more about the ritual mentioned by the cultist you questioned.$B$BThese rituals must be the core of their plans to attack Orgrimmar.$B$BTake one of the robes from the arrested cultists; it\'s not like they\'re going to need them anymore. Put it on and go back to the cultist outpost at the Jaggedswine Farm in Durotar and see what you can learn about these rituals and their place in the cult\'s plans. */ /* objectives: Put on your Recruit\'s Robe, go to the Jaggedswine Farm and get the Book of Incantations from Overseer Jintak. Read from the Book of Incantations near the Cultist Altar to practice the ritual. */ /* offerrewardtext: You need to familiarize yourself with the portal ritual quickly. We\'ve sent dozens of brothers into the city, but only so many can evade capture. We\'re relying on you, $n. */
